als.register(...)`\n- Triggering the signal and verifying handler invocation\n- Restoring previous handlers\n- Enabling JLine trace logging so the internal `toString(...)` path reaches the remaining reflective `Field#get(...)` call sites\n\nI did not run the tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_033d30255e7eb8630169f91f6c08e48190b3d90087a21eb3b7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 689, "output": 658, "cacheRead": 40960, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 42307, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777934176866, "responseId": "resp_033d30255e7eb8630169f91f617f608190a693cf77a2282e3f"}}
